quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  24,1,"Simoore, Men jippinii nde Men farlii nde, Men jippini e nder mayre Aayeeje …ďanngu…óe belajo'o onon on waajitoto"
  24,2,"Debbo jinoowo on e gorko jeenoowo on foccee gooto kala e ma…ď…ďe paatawol(looci) teemedere, wata yurmeende ma…ď…ďe nanngu on e fii Diina Alla kan, si tawii on laatike hi…óon gom…óini Alla e √Ďalaande Laakara nden. Yo seedo foccugol …ďe ngol jamaa immorde e gom…óin…ďe …ďen"
  24,3,"Gorko jinoowo on o resataa si wonaa debbo jeenoowo maa…óum sirkoowo, debbo jinoowo on resatah mo si wanaa gorko jinoowo maa…óum sirkoowo, …óum harminaama e dow gom…óin…ďe …ďen"
  24,4,"E …ďen …ďe no tukka rew…ďe saŇčii…ďe …ďen refti hara …ďe addaali seedee…ďe nayo, haray piyee …ďe paatawol(looci) cappan…óe jeetati. Wata on ja…ďan …ďe seedagol poomaa. ∆Āen …óon, ko kam…ďe woni Faasiqii…ďe …ďen"
  24,5,"Si wanaa …ďen tuubu…ďe …ďaawo …óum …ďe mo∆ī∆īini. Pellet, Alla ko O Surroowo Yurmetee…óo"
  24,6,"E …ďen …ďe no tukka sonnaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen hara laatanaaki …ďe seedee…ďe si wanaa wonkiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin, ko yo go…ó…óo e ma…ď…ďe seedo seedeeji nayi [o woondira] Alla pellet, kanko ko e goongu…ďe …ďen o jeyaa"
  24,7,"Jowa…ďun …óum, wonndema yo kuddi Alla wonu e dow makko si o laatike jeyaa…óo e fenoo…ďe …ďen"
  24,8,"∆Āe dunyira e [sonnaajo on] lepte …óen, nde o seedotoo seedeeji nayi [o woondira] Alla, pellet [gorko on] ko e fenoo…ďe …ďen o jeyaa"
  24,9,"Jowa…ďun …óum, ko nde Alla tikkata e dow makko si [gorko on] laatike ko e goongu…ďe …ďen o jeyaa"
  24,10,"Sinndo wanaano ∆Āural Alla ngal e dow moo…óon e Yurmeende Makko nden, e wonndema Alla ko O ja…ďoowo tuubuubuye √Ďee√Īu…óo"
